\vspace{0.2cm}

\textbf{1. Brainstorming of Product / Service Ideas}
\begin{itemize}
    \item \textbf{Amazon Prime} -- Premium subscription service
    \item \textbf{Netflix} -- Digital streaming service
    \item \textbf{Apple iPhone} -- Premium smartphone product
    \item \textbf{Nike Sports Shoes} -- Branded footwear product
\end{itemize}

\vspace{0.2cm}

\textbf{2. Shortlisting of Idea} \\
I selected Amazon Prime due to its diversified structure combining e-commerce, logistics, and entertainment within a single subscription. The upgraded concept, \textbf{Amazon Prime+}, enhances value through intelligent personalization and service assurance.

\vspace{0.2cm}

\textbf{3. Selected Idea: Amazon Prime+ (Enhanced Model)} \\
Amazon Prime+ builds upon fast delivery, free shipping, Prime Video, and Prime Music. The enhancement introduces a \textbf{Smart Choice Guarantee System}-an AI-driven layer that:
\begin{itemize}
    \item Suggests high-rated, low-return products
    \item Provides priority customer support
    \item Offers instant refund processing
    \item Delivers personalized subscription insights
\end{itemize}
This shifts Prime from a delivery service to a smart decision-support ecosystem.

\vspace{0.2cm}

\textbf{4. Problem Identification} \\
Consumers face decision fatigue, delivery uncertainty, multiple subscriptions, and time inefficiency. These factors reduce convenience and increase indirect costs.

\vspace{0.2cm}

\textbf{5. Need, Want, and Demand Addressed} \\
\textbf{Need:} Convenience, reliability, speed, and simplified digital experiences. \\
\textbf{Want:} Faster and smarter shopping, trusted recommendations, entertainment bundling, and premium assurance benefits. \\
\textbf{Demand:} When customers are willing to pay for enhanced efficiency, personalization, and service guarantee, wants transform into demand. Amazon Prime+ fulfills this demand through an intelligent, integrated, value-added subscription ecosystem.

\vspace{0.2cm}

