\vspace{0.2cm}

The 4Ps Framework for Amazon Prime+ is as follows.


% --- 1-Line Descriptions ---
% --- Strictly 1-Line Humanized Descriptions ---
\textbf{Product:} An all-in-one assistant combining your favorite media with a smarter, stress-free way to shop. \\
\textbf{Price:} A single membership that pays for itself through massive bundled value and total peace of mind. \\
\textbf{Place:} A digital store that lives in your pocket, ready anywhere and backed by a global delivery network. \\
\textbf{Promotion:} Friendly, helpful reminders that meet you where you are to make your daily life a little easier.

